        <h1><a href="http://ucengine.org/">U.C.Engine</a> by <a href="http://af83.com/">af83</a>.</h1>

        <p>U.C.Engine (Unified Collaboration Engine), is a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PubSub">publish/subscribe</a> server with persistence.</p> 
 
<p>It allows you to build real time applications like collaboration based services, live meetings, games or anything that fits well in an event driven philosophy.</p> 
 
<p>U.C.Engine is a <a href="https://github.com/AF83/ucengine/blob/master/AGPL-LICENSE.txt">free software project</a> written in erlang. It exposes a ReSTful HTTP API with JSON as its primary exchange format.</p> 
 
<p>See the <a class="internal present" href="/introduction.html">introduction</a> to learn some of the concepts of U.C.Engine.</p> 
